  "overall": "This character is a 50-year-old female Gnome Sorcerer from Driftwood. They are rangy and about 3 ft 5 in tall. They have white, shaved at the sides hair, hazel eyes, fair skin, a long nose, and a notched ear. By temperament they are wry and dry. They speak with a commanding voice. A characteristic habit: names every animal they meet. They tended an inn’s stables. Survived a collapse in the mines. Born to Everett and Cordelia, a family known for keen map-making. The family secret: a buried family fortune. Given the choice, they favour a long walk, cannot abide unpaid debts, and always take ginger beer. They are driven to make peace with an old enemy, haunted by a fear of betrayal by a friend, and keeping faith with a half-forgotten village rite. They carry a string of river pearls and are accompanied by a homing pigeon."
